SaltProjectImpl
public interface SaltProject
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Salt Project'.

The following features are supported:

  • SCorpus Graphs
  • SName

getSCorpusGraphs

org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<SCorpusGraph> getSCorpusGraphs()
Returns the value of the 'SCorpus Graphs' containment reference list. The list contents are of type SCorpusGraph. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Salt Project'.

If the meaning of the 'SCorpus Graphs' containment reference list isn't clear, there really should be more of a description here...

the value of the 'SCorpus Graphs' containment reference list.

differences

org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<String> differences(Object obj)
Computes differences between this object and the given one and returns all differences in a list as textual descriptions. This method uses the equals method, to check for differences and can be seen as an inverse function to equals().
